des:
Free Speech TV (FSTV) is one of the last standing national, independent news networks committed to advancing progressive social justice. Hear the latest progressive news and politics from the Stephanie Miller Show, Democracy Now!, and more through the Free Speech TV (FSTV) live stream! 

Our lineup includes daily news programs, independent documentaries, special events coverage, election coverage, and more. Nationally syndicated shows include Democracy Now, The Stephanie Miller Show, The Thom Hartmann Program, The Randi Rhodes Show, Rising Up with Sonali, The David Pakman Show, and Gay USA. 

Hear the news as it happens through the live stream is on air 24-hours a day, seven days a week to ensure you are getting the most up-to-date news and information available. 

For more information about Free Speech TV (FSTV) and our programming, please visit FreeSpeech.org.
